Microwave
Heating
Instructions
(Based on 100oW Microwave)
Omin
1. Heat from frozen
2. Peel corner back before heating
3. Place tray in microwave
4.Heat on HIGH for 8 minutes
Important: Microwave ovens vary in
power. Adjust heating time accordingly
To test if meal is property heated, place
hands under the pack; if you feel any
cold spots return to the microwave for
a further 30-60 seconds.
